Class International

java.lang.Object
src.Student
src.NonResident
src.International
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Student>
public class International
extends NonResident
This class, International, extends NonResident as a subclass. Contains methods for checking what tuition should be due for the Student depending on credits enrolled and the toString() method.
Author:
Christian Osma, Liam Smith
